> Nutrient values are representative of a 1/2 pizza. There are 2 servings per container.

Adjust rack to middle position and preheat #oven{} to 350 degrees.

Remove and discard plastic film from @Spinach Artichoke Pizza{1%14.4 ounce}.

Bake pizza on middle rack, ~{15-18%minutes}.

Let pizza stand at least ~{3%minutes} before slicing and serving.